reviewText: good dvd, covers alot of Ireland in just one hour, nice aerial video- could use more video from the ground so you will see true perspective if you plan to visit.
Fantastic tour of Ireland. Stephen very interesting.

I ordered this DVD for my mother-in-law but watched it first.....it was very good and I really enjoyed it......showed very pretty sights in Ireland.  My mother-in-law is of Irish descent and had always wanted to go t Ireland.....she is too old to try to tackle that now and she really enjoyed seeing this DVD!!!!
My sister watched this by renting it at our local library.  She loved it so much I surprised her with it as a gift.  She loves it!!
Loved it. I have ordered another copy for a friend. We both have Irish ancestors and enjoyed the tour very much.
